        "t1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Bauspiel toys transform everyday play into tactile and cognitive development. Their oversized shapes and luminous details help children build towers, castles, and abstract constructions while exercising problem-solving and spatial reasoning. The Lucent Cubes cast colorful light when stacked near a window. Parents tell us these toys make play time feel meaningful: focused, screen-free, and joyfully open-ended.</p>"
