          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Families Choose My Toy Wagon for Bauspiel",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "t3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>We curate Bauspiel because their commitment to non-toxic finishes and sustainably sourced European wood aligns with what we believe a toy should be: safe, beautiful, and built to last. Every Bauspiel order ships from our Los Angeles warehouse, with free shipping on orders $150 and over within the contiguous US. Returns are simple, and customer questions go to a real person on our team.</p>"
