          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p><strong>Bauspiel Lucent Cubes, Set of 100.</strong> 100 transparent, sparkling cubes ideal for light play and architectural design. Non-toxic wood construction, rich textures, and unlimited building potential invite hours of collaborative play.</p><p><strong>Bauspiel Castle Set, 16 pieces.</strong> Wooden elements for building fairy-tale castles and sparking role-play. Geometric pieces develop fine motor skills, spatial orientation, and strength.</p><p><strong>Bauspiel Knight's Castle Extension, 6 pieces.</strong> An add-on featuring knight pieces, towers, walls, and defense barriers. Augments existing castle sets with safe, natural materials for more elaborate storytelling.</p><p><strong>Bauspiel Colour Staircase with Luminous Blocks, 16 pieces.</strong> Stacked color blocks with glowing inserts that teach sequencing, gradients, and balance. Promotes visual tracking and pattern recognition.</p>"
